CODE:
public class Mask {
    public static void main(String[] args){
        for(int i=1;i<=11;i++) {
            for(int j=1;j<=(11-i);j++)
                System.out.print(" ");

            for(int k=1;k<=i;k++)
                System.out.print("*");


            System.out.println("");

        }

    }

}

OUTPUT:




          *
         **
        ***
       ****
      *****
     ******
    *******
   ********
  *********
 **********
***********

Process finished with exit code 0



